Map created by: chickencluc0, ("[BsB] [DP] grenade" ingame)

I created this map on a whim, the idea came to me to have a map with two sides seperated by a valley where the teams had to snipe at one another. And then, this appeared.

The map is nice for having bots compete to the death on, if that's your cup of tea.
